# ContrailCast RMS health broker -- ACL for anonymous clients.
# Install to /etc/mosquitto/aclfile
#
# Lines with no preceding "user" apply to anonymous (un-authenticated) clients.
#
# DEV (current): broad read+write within the stations/ namespace -- keeps topic
# layout flexible while the tool is still evolving.
topic readwrite stations/#

# LATER (zero-friction hardening, no passwords): have the tool connect with
# username == its stationID (it already knows it), then switch to:
#
#   topic   read  stations/#
#   pattern write stations/%u/#
#
# That confines each publisher to its own stations/<stationID>/... subtree and
# stops accidental cross-station overwrites. (It does not stop a malicious actor
# from claiming someone else's username -- that needs per-station secrets.)
